{"tid":115952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次感受到心靈上嘅空虛","createTime":"2017-02-11T03:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T20:45:23.000Z","uid":47496,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa705cbc996f66b17e730887554e1ad10651a723","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:30:09.000Z","msg":"WhatsApp 已經不再跟我說話<br />\n不再向我訴心事<br />\n雖然有點後悔<br />\n但我不後悔令她知道我是愛她，我會等待她<br />\n也許這都是上天的安排和考驗<br />\n我相信時間會證明愛情的"},{"pid":"7ebcff38b14638e959bd517c5e02306b51bad57d","tid":115952,"uid":77251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"我尋日都畀男神收咗朋友卡<br />\n共勉之"},{"pid":"f353f45eb5c67958e1cd80b674b7ec5e702dc39c","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"有d野都叫做大家經歷過<br />\n以為大家有感覺<br />\n反而只係自己一廂情願<br />\n感情就係咁殘酷？<br />\n如果有時光機可以回到過去<br />\n我希望唔想同佢講番果段說話<br />\n如果有魔法師<br />\n我希望佢可以消除果晚嘅記憶<br />\n如果有機會可以挽回愛情<br />\n我希望可以折壽十年作為代價"},{"pid":"af3157cbbd2979aff3893fea6733c21419c7837e","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我尋日都畀男神收咗朋友卡<br />\n共勉之</blockquote><br />\n佢係咪已經有女朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我係有女朋友<br />\n對其他女仔都只視作為朋友<br />\n就算只係一廂情願未做女朋友<br />\n我對其他女仔都不感興趣"},{"pid":"325192e3d519033a4f8c0625e341917d9027b3c7","tid":115952,"uid":39886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:21:24.000Z","msg":"做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdebb74ee5289f163cd3419ee812dc8939c9ac66","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T04:53:15.000Z","msg":"臨近情人節先咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1194ea2b554185acc018edb4847cdefd3d9a68c9","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T05:49:46.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14439e4f4ed091ca5cde3009f60120005c94f9b","tid":115952,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"Agger 好耐冇見過佢冇搵過佢 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f226bfef03570604a325cea906037e787ab407ca","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agger 好耐冇見過佢冇搵過佢 好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢係咪仲健康開心咁生活緊呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3677609c2d86c72fa96a8a36926c6a2886e50c8","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209f197c970becef5731fcbda58f9d77e2f3d326","tid":115952,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:08:07.000Z","msg":"咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ae741ef6aa16c2b990d0eb3e2c53267ae947be","tid":115952,"uid":47496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:45:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都幾晚訓唔著<br />\n開眼就眼濕濕<br />\n合眼就流眼淚<br />\n好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}